<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4892934>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Margarinotus ephemeralis and Margarinotus remotus, median lobe of aedeagus. A. M. ephemeralis, dorsal view.B.M. ephemeralis, lateral view.C. M. ephemeralis, apical view of gonopore. D. M. remotus, apical view of gonopore. E. M. remotus, dorsal view. F. M. remotus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4892934/files/figure.png" ;
